description: [``botocore``] This release adds support for updating and deleting spaces and projects in Amazon CodeCatalyst. It also adds support for creating, getting, and deleting source repositories in CodeCatalyst projects.
[``botocore``] This release adds the ability to assign a case to a queue or user.
[``botocore``] Update lexv2-models client to latest version
[``botocore``] This release adds support for Route 53 On Outposts, a new feature that allows customers to run Route 53 Resolver and Resolver endpoints locally on their Outposts.
[``botocore``] Improve performance of S3 clients by simplifying and optimizing endpoint resolution.
[``botocore``] Cross account support for SageMaker Feature Store
[``botocore``] Cross account support for SageMaker Feature Store
[``botocore``] Adding support for Tags on Create and Resource Tagging API.
[``botocore``] Added API argument --toxicity-detection to startTranscriptionJob API, which allows users to view toxicity scores of submitted audio.
